6:14:38.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363474\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363474</a><br />\n與此同時,LIHKG香港女神總會盃非聯賽參賽女神提名亦都已經展開,截止提名期為17年9月4日0時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S 第一場完結係聽晚10點01,太趕改漏左"},{"pid":"f9f99c9802ea79cc0092911810e51e565cc06b10","tid":374334,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71ddc8c0ebc7fa5d7c354bd8c69b7fcc965e4b1","tid":374334,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"依家唔得閒,有無人推"},{"pid":"f1d750c840b83ab70f5fc41d35cda931accf9471","tid":374334,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家唔得閒,有無人推</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f341d3cd8631470838d957e23738d33948730902","tid":374334,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家唔得閒,有無人推</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"h